BLAWhat is movierok?
=================

movierok is an open database for movie rips.

movierok helps you organize your movies:

    * browse them online
    * find them faster
    * search for them
    * start them with one click
    * see which movies your friends have


movierok ..

    * uses omdb.org for movie information
    * is user-driven like wikipedia or omdb.org
    * works like musicbrainz but for movies
    * will always remain free and open
    * needs you to install a firefox extension
    * provides webservices so other programs can use it
    * already counts 1425 rips


sign up and send us your feedback to feedback@movierok.org 

http://movierok.org/
